text: Katrina Kaif (, born Katrina Turquotte, 16 July 1983) is an English actress and model. She was born in Hong Kong. Kaif stars in Bollywood movies. Her first well known works were the Bollywood comedies Maine Pyaar Kyun Kiya? (2005) and Namastey London (2007). She also starred as Zoya "Zee" Humaimi in Ek Tha Tiger (2012) and the sequel Tiger Zinda Hai (2017). Later she appeared in Thugs of Hindostan (2018), Zero (2018), Bharat (2019) and Sooryavanshi (2019). == Other websites == ==References== Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:English movie actors Category:English television actors Category:English models
